title: Mathematics Through Paper Folding by Alton T. Olson (.pdf)
description:
Mathematics Through Paper Folding by Alton T. Olson

Requirements: .PDF reader, 2.7 mb

Overview: Paper folding not only simplifies the learning of mathematics it also builds an experiential base necessary for further learning. The exercises in this publication, appropriate at various grade levels, lead students to discover and demonstrate such mathematical relationships as reflections, transformations, and symmetry.

Genre: Non-Fiction > Educational
